name: 20190803college-careers
comment: We hosted a Design Thinking workshop for College and Careers 2019. Howard Shyng, Ting Zhu, Jacob Kinley, Sierra Skorupski and Mick McQuaid helped four groups of high school juniors and seniors to design a phone app to assist with New Year's Resolutions. The workshop was previously designed by Cynthia Zachar, Joe Agnelli, and Bakari Wilkins for Getting Connected 2019.
